How to install Python, Qt, and PyQt on MacOS 10.6.4 (64-bit).

<ol>
    <li>Get macports</li>
    <li>Install Python 3.1.3, using the online download at Python's website.</li>
    <li>In Terminal, type:
<pre>sudo port install py31-pyqt4</pre>
</li>
